Program: Great Lives
Title: Sir Donald Wolfit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b049jl17
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 16 Feb 2018
Humphrey Carpenter invites the famous to discuss deceased heroes. This week Ned Sherrin on Sir Donald Wolfit. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? From 2002. Show less